      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "Debian 9 ships GCC 6.3 according to [the development packages listing](https://packages.debian.org/oldstable/devel/). GCC 6 is [listed as supporting some features of C++17 experimentally](https://gcc.gnu.org/gcc-6/changes.html).\r\n\r\nUbuntu Xenial ships with a [default GCC 5.3](https://packages.ubuntu.com/xenial/gcc), which is even older. A PPA offers newer GCC versions: [~ubuntu-toolchain-r](https://launchpad.net/~ubuntu-toolchain-r/+archive/ubuntu/test?field.series_filter=xenial) ",
